### Client Endpoints Testing File

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@clientId = CLIENT_ID_HERE
@clientName = Empresa XYZ S.L.
@clientCif = A87654321

---

## CLIENT CRUD

### 1. Crear cliente - POST /api/client
POST {{baseUrl}}/client
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{clientName}}",
  "cif": "{{clientCif}}",
  "email": "contacto@empresaxyz.com",
  "phone": "+34912345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Avenida Tecnológica",
    "number": "123",
    "postal": "28050",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

### 2. Listar clientes - GET /api/client
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 3. Listar clientes con filtro por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?page=1&limit=10&name=Empresa
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Listar clientes con ordenamiento
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?page=1&limit=10&sort=createdAt
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 5. Obtener cliente específico - GET /api/client/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 6. Actualizar cliente - PUT /api/client/:id
PUT {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Empresa XYZ Actualizada",
  "cif": "A87654321",
  "email": "nuevo@empresaxyz.com",
  "phone": "+34912345679",
  "address": {
    "street": "Avenida Nueva",
    "number": "456",
    "postal": "28051",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

### 7. Archivar cliente (soft delete) - DELETE /api/client/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}?soft=true
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 8. Eliminar cliente (hard delete) - DELETE /api/client/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}?soft=false
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 9. Listar clientes archivados - GET /api/client/archived
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/archived?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 10. Restaurar cliente archivado - PATCH /api/client/:id/restore
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}/restore
Authorization: {{authToken}}
